    Product description

    Elevate your dining experience with this exquisite marble top pedestal dining set. The round marble tabletop exudes elegance and sophistication, while the sleek pedestal base in a gleaming metallic finish adds a touch of modern flair. Complementing the table are the plush velvet-upholstered chairs, featuring a tufted design and tapered legs for a refined look. This dining set effortlessly combines luxury and comfort, making it a stunning centrepiece for your dining room or open-concept living space. With its timeless style and high-quality construction, this set promises to be a cherished investment that will elevate your home's aesthetic for years to come.
